Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st0808

ST 0808: Ancillary Text Metadata Sets.

This standard (ST) defines the Ancillary Text Local Set and the Ancillary Text Universal Set.

These sets include KLV metadata elements for encoding text data that may be associated with Motion Imagery data. Including descriptive text along with Motion Imagery supports additional capabilities, such as search and discovery, as well as providing valuable context information about the Motion Imagery data
